docs/qa/DEEP_SCAN_REPORT.md:246:### 2026-03-12 Backend Optimize Phase 0 Baseline Hotspots
docs/qa/DEEP_SCAN_REPORT.md:257:  - `OPT-P1-001` first because it is response-local, contract-neutral, and directly reduces query fan-out on customer booking detail and update flows.
docs/qa/DEEP_SCAN_REPORT.md:258:  - `OPT-P1-002` second because partner dashboard endpoints are repeated operational reads and the current implementation multiplies queries per request.
