  • Replace partner stats and rating histogram loops with DB-side aggregates
  • Consolidate admin payment review queue summary counts/amounts
  • Add targeted regression tests for query shape and response behavior
  • Refresh backlog/atlas/run summary docs and advance the run to the next phase
