    60	
    61	## Partner Booking Fulfillment APIs
    62	| Surface | Endpoints | Request contract | Response contract | Service/modules | Notes |
    63	| --- | --- | --- | --- | --- | --- |
    64	| Booking queues and detail | `/bookings/get_all_booking_detail_for_partner/`, `/bookings/get_booking_detail_by_booking_number/` | `partner_session_token` plus queue filters such as `booking_status`, `workflow_bucket`, `booking_number` | Partner list/detail booking serializers with workflow fields | `booking/manage_partner_booking.py`, `booking/querysets.py`, `booking/serializers.py` | Queue visibility depends on minimum payment approval and issue state. |
    65	| Operator actions | `/bookings/partner_action_for_booking/`, `/bookings/update_booking_status_into_close/`, `/bookings/update_booking_status_into_report_rabbit/` | Partner token, booking number, action/status data | Updated booking detail | `booking/manage_partner_booking.py`, `booking/workflow.py` | Operator actions and admin payment review must stay aligned with workflow transitions. |
